{"tid":2150851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買蘋果報紙唔夠，最好訂閱埋，啱啱我又說服到一個巴打訂咗500蚊蘋果","createTime":"2020-08-11T06:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T06:24:19.000Z","uid":65328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1ff0a478f94ec6929072858739ef1365b7d5a7","tid":2150851,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZSPxJA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZSPxJA.png&h=7115ce3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原先我同阿仙奴世界第一#22506嘈緊買報紙送俾藍絲成疊扔落垃圾桶好戇鳩<br />\n點知佢話要用500蚊訂閱蘋果，<br />\n<br />\n真漢子<br />\n<br />\n我就對事不對人，佢做得好地方我一定幫佢宣揚<br />\n<br />\n好事唔怕傳千里<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日賺咗錢既巴絲請將部份收益訂閱蘋果撐蘋果<br />\n<br />\n蘋果繼續做落去你地既股票可以繼續升，winwin"},{"pid":"df551cc4483a99d6eea2f1a6086c0ca4a9180705","tid":2150851,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"一齊訂"},{"pid":"cc38e2b81a1fac1541d4876ddab97e2b4697ce1c","tid":2150851,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"利申，並無持有蘋果股票<br />\n<br />\n非打手"},{"pid":"294dfb23ff2815940f43741c0537f5ab03b0ac06","tid":2150851,"uid":106882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c81gXgg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc81gXgg.png&h=3b6952d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8d74d5688958e784a9ab3cd20870cc2e63c1122","tid":2150851,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"294dfb23ff2815940f43741c0537f5ab03b0ac06","tid":2150851,"uid":106882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c81gXgg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc81gXgg.png&h=3b6952d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"又多一個巴打支持蘋果"},{"pid":"445a756b88f9a739eb0a6b